%N A397320 Prime numbers p such that p^2 divides 40^(p-1) - 1.
%C A397320 a(5) = 7036306088681 is from Fischer's tables. No more terms up to 2*10^14.
%H A397320 Richard Fischer, <a href="http://www.fermatquotient.com/FermatQuotienten/FermQ_Sort.txt">Fermatquotienten von 2 bis 1052</a>, Dec 19 2019.
